    "title": "Marketplace Manager - Delhivery - Immediate Joiners Preferred",
    "description": "Delhivery invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Marketplace Manager at our Vadodara location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Delhivery:\nDelhivery is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Delhivery!",
